HAI 1.4
    HOW IZ I power YR base AN YR exp
        I HAS A result ITZ 1
        I HAS A i ITZ 0
        IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN exp
            result R PRODUKT OF result AN base
        IM OUTTA YR loop
        FOUND YR result
    IF U SAY SO

    VISIBLE "2^10 = " AN I IZ power YR 2 AN YR 10 MKAY
    VISIBLE "3^5 = " AN I IZ power YR 3 AN YR 5 MKAY
KTHXBYE
